Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…永遠普遍の愛なんて　信じられるのかしら？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:35.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い紅茶に溶かす　ため息模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:39.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　待ちくたびれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:48.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを追いかけて　堕ちるワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまで行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}イロトリドリの闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:02.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道標の旋律　心が騒ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時計仕掛けの運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:10.06,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊してしまえ　私は自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが真実
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze　生きる証
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…是否能相信  所谓永恒的爱？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:35.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叹息溶化于甘美红茶  化为波纹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:39.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已经  再也按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:48.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追寻着你  坠落往  Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何处才是尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}穿越色彩斑斓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:02.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指明前路的旋律  踊动不已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假使命运如时钟般不可逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:10.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破坏它  我将获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是唯一的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze  是我生存的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹·贝萨流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以定罪枷锁之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此  对你做出裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是你的存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体被拖拽着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑色的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:25.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的孩子和黑色的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…这里到底是什么鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管跑到哪  都是一样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是在做恶梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说只要有人犯了重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯就会派使者前来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  是来把这小鬼关进阿比斯的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  少爷  这位大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  基尔  千万别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…  那到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个扑克  居然这么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是我先看上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就说过了  这家伙可是我的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许对他出手  死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我性骚扰的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被那种低级灵体玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵体？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是诞生在阿比斯中的生命体的总称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中扑克是很低等的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是灵体吗  染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵体都有袭击人的习性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到你的时候  你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…  绝对不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要杀我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  你在胡说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从死神手中救了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是记错人了  真是个失礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  别把我和扑克那种东西混为一谈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～太好了～发现饼干了耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已经饿到快不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个奇怪的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还那么慌张的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不怕我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯这个空间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看到许多不可思议的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说早点接受现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能清楚地把握现状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我被绑架的时候  奥斯卡叔叔说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种时候最要紧的是  保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你不是我的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才又救了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经大条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  只不过是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像黑兔子  染血黑兔这种名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是别人给我乱起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特别允许你叫我艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有种很熟悉的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是  不要误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救你是有目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是为了你着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得死神把你丢进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便死掉的话  我可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你想要我做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想逃出阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一直在等像你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够成为我的契约者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也觉察到了吧  这里不是一般的监牢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯与你所在的世界是两个不同次元的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同次元？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两个世界之间产生了被称为通路的空间扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的力量在那里强制打开出口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我和你就都可以从这里出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在的我力量受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发挥不出足以打开出口的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够解除力量限制的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要喊我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意契约就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有必须去做的事  我要从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你也想从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就让我们联手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才如果和她握手的话  会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心  奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来接您的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹大人被关进这里以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱因兹华斯家就立刻派人来救您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到消息后  很担心您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那前面  有可以传送出去的魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油  很快就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在想那个灵体的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  没有在想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是众多灵体中  最危险的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓契约  是指其存在本身不安定的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了持续地存在于我们的世界  所必需的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那家伙在成人仪式时现身了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是靠这里传过去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时现身而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候她那么强…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也发生过  每次通路被打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都会出现并干涉我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把自己选中的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:15:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是打算在最后杀掉奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那个了  我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的确是很不讲道理  很可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她救了我两次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说些什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关那家伙的事  我完全不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉她不像是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…我会有这种想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么呀  奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢  我这人真是…啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝不仅对你表现出杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对着你大喊要杀了你不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样还觉得她不是坏人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道艾莉丝的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特别允许你叫我艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  艾莉丝要杀我这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还想再多玩一会儿的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  爱给人添麻烦的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙叫疯婴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种能窥视并玩弄人类记忆的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵我手的时候  犹豫了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那女孩倒是很听话  立马就被牵走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里死掉的话  我可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么你要做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你  我完全不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要一定要选择我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对呢  我也是  对你一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就在我挣扎着想要出去时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了那个怀表的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到很熟悉的旋律  就追了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就来到你身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我就觉察到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个  能够带我逃出阿比斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何根据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是相信自己的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能解除限制的话  这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要救她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道她有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道刚才的话是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的人情还没还呢  怎么能让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我脑子不正常了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在这里失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝  我要与你订下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了哟  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是请您与我订下契约  才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思维停止  身体在拒绝在反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法抵抗的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在体内蹂躏着…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该为能够成为我的东西而感到荣幸  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…终于到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下力量的限制解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逃离阿比斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是…太令人惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他靠自己的力量从阿比斯逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从结果来看这样不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得到萨布耶里特的悲剧之钥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  已经没有退路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这位大人  是会带来毁灭的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那只黑兔子现在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}通路……要连接上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}现在你也是一个名符其实的「违法契约者」了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}还记得的  就只有艾莉丝这个名字……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不要再伤害艾莉丝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}这是在试探我吗……很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  晨晖映照之地